T1  - Random Coefficients on Endogenous Variables in Simultaneous Equations Models
PY  - 2018
Y1  - 2018/04/01
DO  - 10.1093/restud/rdx047
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 85
IS  - 2
SP  - 1193
